United Nations Plane Crashes in Congo, Killing Passengers, Spokesman Says

-- B y   F r a n z   W i l d
-- 
2011-04-04T15:23:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-04/united-nations-plane-crashes-in-congo-killing-passengers-spokesman-says.html
A United Nations plane crashed while
attempting to land in Democratic Republic of Congo’s capital,
Kinshasa, killing some passengers, Madnodje Mounoubai, a
spokesman for the UN’s peacekeeping mission in the country, said
by phone from the city today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Franz Wild in Johannesburg at 
